metadata.name: Afternoon Flocks
metadata.description:
Early afternoon at Collpa Colorado. Massive flocks of macaws, parrots and parrotlets gather to consume the exposed clay.

Recorded on April 12, 2023 using a baffled, spaced pair of LOM UÅ¡i Pro microphones fed into a Zoom F3 recorder. Site assistance provided by Jair Mariche.
